---  HIGHLIGHT IMPORTANT RELEASE AND PACKAGING INFORMATION ------- May 2013 ---
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following options are used in third party applications:

  --input, -i
  --output, -o
  -encoding, -u
  --font
  --font-size
  --force
  --line-numbers, -l
  --replace-tabs, -t
  --syntax
  --out-format
  --include-style
  --inline-css
  --style
  --failsafe
  --validate-input

The following themes are used in third party applications:
  - bclear (Evolution)
  
See the makefiles and INSTALL for packaging information.